{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/10-film-tentang-time-traveling-ini-wajib-kamu-tonton-yang-ke-8-dari-indonesia-loh/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"10 Film Tentang Time Traveling Ini Wajib Kamu Tonton. Yang ke 8 Dari Indonesia Loh!","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Perjalanan waktu/<em>time travel</em>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ini adalah impian manusia yang masih belum kesampaian. Saat perjalanan meninggalkan planet Bumi dan menuju semesta lain semakin terasa mungkin dan masuk akal, tapi perjalanan menuju masa lalu maupun masa depan masih berupa sebatas fiksi ilmiah. Tidak terhitung banyaknya novel ataupun film yang mencoba menggambarkan perjalanan yang tidak pernah terjadi ataupun dilakukan oleh manusia ini. Berbagai teori mengemuka soal bisa tidaknya perjalanan menembus waktu. Tapi tetap saja, <em>time traveling</em> adalah impian liar umat manusia yang belum terbukti dapat dilakukan dalam kenyataan.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Walau belum bisa melakukannya di dunia nyata, tapi film-film berikut ini mencoba menunjukkan bagaimana seandainya perjalanan menembus waktu itu mungkin dilakukan.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Timecop (1994)</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Film ini dibintangi aktor laga yang terkenal jagoan <em>split</em> (merentangkan kedua kaki ke samping hingga sejajar dengan permukaan), Jean-Claude Van Damme. Dari judulnya kita bisa menebak kalau ceritanya pasti soal polisi yang berurusan dengan waktu/perjalanan waktu. Film ini termasuk film tersukses dari Van Damme, dan yang paling sedikit mendapatkan review jelek dari kritikus.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41403\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41403\" data-attachment-id=\"41403\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/10-film-tentang-time-traveling-ini-wajib-kamu-tonton-yang-ke-8-dari-indonesia-loh/attachment/traveling1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Adegan fenomenal film Timecop. Sumber gambar: bulletproofaction.com\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling1.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41403 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling1.jpg\" alt=\"Adegan fenomenal film Timecop. Sumber gambar: bulletproofaction.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41403\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Adegan fenomenal film Timecop. Sumber gambar: bulletproofaction.com</p></div></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Terminator 2: Judgment Day (1991)</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Merupakan sekuel dari Terminator (1984), film ini menceritakan perjuangan seorang ibu dan anak menghadapi cyborg pembunuh dari masa depan yang mengincar nyawa si anak. Mereka mendapatkan bantuan dari cyborg lain, juga dari masa depan, dimana cyborg ini dulunya mengincar nyawa si ibu. Film dengan quote terkenal “I’ll be back” ini adalah legenda. Wajib nonton minimal sekali.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41404\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41404\" data-attachment-id=\"41404\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/10-film-tentang-time-traveling-ini-wajib-kamu-tonton-yang-ke-8-dari-indonesia-loh/attachment/traveling2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Adegan baku tembak seru. Sumber gambar: businessinsider.com\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling2.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41404 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling2.jpg\" alt=\"Adegan baku tembak seru. Sumber gambar: businessinsider.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41404\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Adegan baku tembak seru. Sumber gambar: businessinsider.com</p></div></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Bill &amp; Ted’s Excellent Adventure (1989)</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Keanu Reeves (pemeran Neo di trilogy The Matrix) bermain di film komedi gokil bertema time travel ini loh! Di masa depan, tepatnya tahun 2688 Futuristic City, dunia berada dalam kondisi utopia yang sempurna berkat inspirasi Two Great Ones, yakni Bill Preston dan Ted Logan. Pemerintah di masa itu mengirimkan seseorang ke tahun 1988 di California dengan mesin waktu berwujud box telepon umum (ingat ini film tahun 1989 dimana telepon selular belum digunakan) untuk memastikan kalau Bill dan Ted lulus sekolah (karena Bill dan Ted merupakan siswa slenge’an malas belajar dan hanya doyan bermain band/musik). Film ini sukses memadukan komedi, fiksi ilmiah dan sedikit drama.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41406\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41406\" data-attachment-id=\"41406\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/10-film-tentang-time-traveling-ini-wajib-kamu-tonton-yang-ke-8-dari-indonesia-loh/attachment/traveling3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Dua remaja hobi nge-band males belajar. Sumber gambar: consequenceofsound.net\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling3.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41406 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling3.jpg\" alt=\"Dua remaja hobi nge-band males belajar. Sumber gambar: consequenceofsound.net\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41406\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dua remaja hobi nge-band males belajar. Sumber gambar: consequenceofsound.net</p></div></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Army of Darkness (1993)</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pegawai supermarket tersedot portal waktu dan terjebak di tahun 1300. Disana dia terpaksa berurusan dengan pasukan tentara zombie yang mengacau situasi. Untungnya saat terbawa ke masa lalu, pegawai ini membawa gergaji mesin dan shotgun bersamanya. Film komedi gelap dengan elemen <em>time travel</em>, okultisme dan elemen-elemen hiburan khas B-movie.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41408\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41408\" data-attachment-id=\"41408\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/10-film-tentang-time-traveling-ini-wajib-kamu-tonton-yang-ke-8-dari-indonesia-loh/attachment/traveling4-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling4-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"“Boomstick!” Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling4-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling4-1.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41408 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling4-1.jpg\" alt=\"“Boomstick!” Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling4-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling4-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41408\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">“Boomstick!” Sumber gambar: youtube.com</p></div></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Men In Black 3 (2012)</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Time travel lekat dengan teknologi canggih, yang mungkin saja dimiliki <em>alien from outer space</em>. Iya ‘kan? Di film Men in Black 3, Agent J di tahun 2009 harus melakukan perjalanan waktu dengan teknologi alien ke tahun 1969 demi mencegah terbunuhnya partner dia, Agent K, di era tersebut. Film ini merupakan film tersukses dari ketiga film Men in Black yang pernah di produksi, meraup keuntungan lebih dari US$624 juta dengan modal US$215 juta.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41409\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41409\" data-attachment-id=\"41409\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/10-film-tentang-time-traveling-ini-wajib-kamu-tonton-yang-ke-8-dari-indonesia-loh/attachment/traveling5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Penjaga Bumi dari serangan alien jahat. Sumber gambar: empireonline.com\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling5.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41409 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling5.jpg\" alt=\"Penjaga Bumi dari serangan alien jahat. Sumber gambar: empireonline.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41409\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Penjaga Bumi dari serangan alien jahat. Sumber gambar: empireonline.com</p></div></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Back to the Future 2 (1989)</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trilogi film Back to the Future memang soal perjalanan menembus waktu. Marty dan Doc harus ‘kembali ke masa depan’ untuk menyelamatkan putra Marty dari kemungkinan masuk penjara. Tapi situasi jadi kacau karena ulah Biff Tannen. Yang menarik adalah penggambaran masa depan (tahun 2015) di film itu, dimana tahun 2015 dunia sudah semakin canggih jika dibandingkan tahun 1989. Namun tentu saja 2015 yang asli tidak seperti yang digambarkan di film Back to the Future 2.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41410\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41410\" data-attachment-id=\"41410\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/10-film-tentang-time-traveling-ini-wajib-kamu-tonton-yang-ke-8-dari-indonesia-loh/attachment/traveling6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tidak ada Hoverboard di tahun 2015 kita. Sumber gambar: io9.gizmodo.com\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling6.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41410 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling6.jpg\" alt=\"Tidak ada Hoverboard di tahun 2015 kita. Sumber gambar: io9.gizmodo.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41410\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tidak ada Hoverboard di tahun 2015 kita. Sumber gambar: io9.gizmodo.com</p></div></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Kate &amp; Leopold (2001)</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kisah cinta berbalut perjalanan menembus waktu. Leopold yang berasal dari tahun 1870 terdampar di tahun 2001. Karakternya yang nyebelin membuat jengkel semua orang, sampai dia bertemu (dan jatuh cinta dengan Kate). Film ini cocok ditonton bareng orang tersayang bro sis.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41411\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41411\" data-attachment-id=\"41411\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/10-film-tentang-time-traveling-ini-wajib-kamu-tonton-yang-ke-8-dari-indonesia-loh/attachment/traveling7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Leopold yang bingung dengan perubahan. Sumber gambar: e-nviromentalist.com\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling7.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41411 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling7.jpg\" alt=\"Leopold yang bingung dengan perubahan. Sumber gambar: e-nviromentalist.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41411\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Leopold yang bingung dengan perubahan. Sumber gambar: e-nviromentalist.com</p></div></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Glitch: Tersesat Dalam Waktu (2009)</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Saya sangat mengapresiasi film Indonesia yang satu ini. Walau akting pemainnya masih perlu polesan lagi, serta Special FX yang masih sederhana, film fiksi ilmiah buatan sineas Indonesia ini merupakan terobosan penting dari tema film Indonesia yang masih berputar di horor, komedi ataupun drama keluarga. Sutradara David Poernomo punya visi dan imajinasi yang keren dan bisa dia eksekusi walau hasilnya tidak memuaskan. Film ini bercerita tentang kekacauan waktu 6 jam sebelum terjadinya tsunami 26 Desember 2004 (pukul 01:58 WIB). Empat sahabat terjebak dalam vortex waktu dan mengalami kejadian-kejadian yang sulit diterima secara akal.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41412\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41412\" data-attachment-id=\"41412\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/10-film-tentang-time-traveling-ini-wajib-kamu-tonton-yang-ke-8-dari-indonesia-loh/attachment/traveling8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Film dengan premise oke. Sumber gambar: ngomongin-film-indonesia.blogspot.com\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling8.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41412 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling8.jpg\" alt=\"Film dengan premise oke. Sumber gambar: ngomongin-film-indonesia.blogspot.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41412\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Film dengan premise oke. Sumber gambar: ngomongin-film-indonesia.blogspot.com</p></div></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Interstellar (2014)</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Film fiksi ilmiah epik ini juga bertema soal time traveling. Di masa depan, lingkungan dunia semakin rusak sehingga manusia mulai mencari lokasi lain sebagai tempat tinggal. Sekelompok astronot tersedot <em>wormhole</em> yang ada di luar angkasa dan perjalanan menembus ruang serta waktu terjadi. Film ini juga memiliki muatan drama yang oke. Hubungan ayah dan putrinya yang sempat rusak dan berakhir dramatis. Dibintangi oleh aktor peraih Piala Oscar Matthew McConaughey.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41413\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41413\" data-attachment-id=\"41413\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/10-film-tentang-time-traveling-ini-wajib-kamu-tonton-yang-ke-8-dari-indonesia-loh/attachment/traveling9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/traveling9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Poster film Interstellar. Sumber gambar: therealsasha.wordpress.com\" data-image-descrip